{"end_time": "2026-05-05T09:26:55Z", "reviewed_units": [{"guideline_id": "rust/no-magic-values.md", "outcome": {"finding_source": "new", "status": "fixed", "summary": "** Moved inspector bounds and other non-self-evident tuning values into the owning constants modules for `camera`, `light`, `selection`, and `selection/dimension_lock`, added a new [`crates/hana/src/movable/core/constants.rs`](/Users/natemccoy/rust/hana_style_fix/crates/hana/src/movable/core/constants.rs), and updated call sites to import those names. For the single-file demo target, kept the exception from `no-magic-values.md` and moved scene/runtime tuning into top-of-file constants in [`demos/wasm_node_demo/src/main.rs`](/Users/natemccoy/rust/hana_style_fix/demos/wasm_node_demo/src/main.rs) instead of creating a new module; the WASM color node constants also absorbed the HSV and clamp literals."}}, {"guideline_id": "rust/spell-out-names.md", "outcome": {"finding_source": "new", "reason": "** rust-analyzer `findReferences` was not reliable for these locals during the pass (one timeout, one empty result), so I used crate-wide `rg` searches to confirm both identifiers were local-only before renaming them.", "status": "fixed", "summary": "** Renamed `max_xz_dist` to `max_ground_plane_distance` in [`crates/hana/src/camera/grid_gizmo.rs`](/Users/natemccoy/rust/hana_style_fix/crates/hana/src/camera/grid_gizmo.rs) and `p0r0` to `plane_origin_to_ray_origin` in [`crates/hana/src/movable/position.rs`](/Users/natemccoy/rust/hana_style_fix/crates/hana/src/movable/position.rs), then updated their immediate uses in the same expressions."}}], "start_time": "2026-05-05T08:10:52Z"}
